  "description": "Configures standardized Windows 11 power and energy management settings for manufacturing workstations and shared production devices. The policy prioritizes operational stability by preventing unexpected sleep or hibernate while plugged in, while still applying reasonable display timeout and battery-related settings for compatible devices. Secure wake behavior is enforced by requiring user authentication after resume. Lid close behavior is intentionally not configured for fixed workstation scenarios.",
